{"article_id":"mnL6XHILfLwXDb3x","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A pharmacy worker shows pills of hydroxychloroquine","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"used to treat the coronavirus","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"at the CHR Centre Hospitalier Regional de la Citadelle Hospital in Liege , Belgium , April 22 , 2020 .","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"( Yves Herman/Reuters )","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"The president claims","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"he ' s taking it as a prophylactic .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"The media met that with hysteria instead of conscientious coverage .","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"President Donald Trump claims","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"that he ' s taking hydroxychloroquine as a preventive measure against contracting coronavirus ,","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"and that he has taken zinc and antibiotic azithromycin as well .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"There ' s no consensus","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"that hydroxychloroquine is an effective therapeutic treatment for COVID-19","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"( early studies have yielded different results ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"and the NIH recently began a controlled clinical trial ) .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Few people","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"I ' ve read","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"argue","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"that it ' s a useful prophylactic .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Nevertheless , the frenzied and childish reaction to Trump ' s championing what amounts to a commonly used prescription drug","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"is more destructive than his annoying habit","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"of bringing it up .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"A CNN columnist warns of \" the danger in Trump ' s decision","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"to self-medicate. \"","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"If Trump is taking the drug ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"it ' s been prescribed","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"and presumably he ' s being monitored ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"yet the CNN piece tries to create impression","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that the president is popping hydroxychloroquine tablets like mints","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to soothe his anxieties .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Senate Democratic leader Chuck Schumer called Trump ' s remarks about hydroxychloroquine \" dangerous , \"","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"though for the general public , the drug itself is no more dangerous than a vast number of pharmaceuticals","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"used every day by millions of Americans","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"to help them live with less pain","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"or to keep them alive .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"\" Side effects of hydroxychloroquine include paranoia , hallucinations and psychosis , \"","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"notes the New York Times ' Michelle Goldberg ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"reading one of the many rare side effects of the drug .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Wait","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"until she reads the warning labels on the abortifacients","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that she wants the government to subsidize .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"For that matter , we ' re often lectured","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"that killing an unborn baby is a decision","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"made solely by a woman in conjunction with her doctor .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"Yet taking hydroxychloroquine is apparently a joint decision between a man , his doctor , every Democrat in congress , all the anchors on CNN , and an entire slate of New York Times op-ed columnists .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"The most reckless media personality on the issue has been Trump ' s former bestie , Joe Scarborough ,","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"who repeatedly told his audience this morning","depth":15},{"id":46,"text":"that hydroxychloroquine will \" kill you \" :","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"So he is not taking something","depth":15},{"id":48,"text":"that his own administration has said","depth":16},{"id":49,"text":"will kill you .","depth":16},{"id":50,"text":"That his own FDA said","depth":16},{"id":51,"text":"will kill you .","depth":16},{"id":52,"text":"That the [ Department of Veterans Affairs ] said","depth":16},{"id":53,"text":"will kill you . ...","depth":16},{"id":54,"text":"That ' s what doctors will say , too .","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"The FDA said ,","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"take it","depth":17},{"id":57,"text":"if you ' re in the hospital","depth":17},{"id":58,"text":"or take it","depth":17},{"id":59,"text":"if you ' re in a closely watched clinical trial .","depth":17},{"id":60,"text":"But , don ' t take it","depth":15},{"id":61,"text":"unless you ' re under those two circumstances .","depth":15},{"id":62,"text":"So the president is not taking it ,","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"and yet , and yet , he ' s telling Americans","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"that they should take it .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Not a single one of these agencies says","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"hydroxychloroquine \" will kill you. \"","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"That would be asinine .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"What the FDA recently noted is that there are elevated risks","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"associated with COVID-19 patients","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"taking the medication ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"which is entirely different .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"As far as I know ,","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"Trump has never explicitly instructed Americans to take it .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"What I do know is that hundreds of thousands of young people","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"who use the drug ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"often to save their lives ,","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"are hearing media personalities and politicians liken it to cyanide .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"Hundreds of thousands of older men and women","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"who take hydroxychloroquine for rheumatoid arthritis","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"are hearing media personalities and politicians telling them","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"their lives are danger .","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"The conscientious way","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"to cover Trump ' s hydroxychloroquine usage","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"would be to point out","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"that there ' s no proof","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"that the drug will help treat the coronavirus ,","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"though tests are still ongoing .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Instead , we are subjected to an overwrought lecture series of nasty , childish , partisan attacks and misleading stories about a couple","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"ingesting fish-tank cleaner .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"\" I would rather he not be taking something","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"that has not been approved by the scientists , especially in his age group , and in his ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"shall we say ,","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"weight group :","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"' Morbidly obese , '","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"they say , \"","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"says House speaker Nancy Pelosi to Anderson Cooper .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Now , it should be noted that there are all kinds of side effects to commonly used drugs .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"Take , for instance , the anti-wrinkle drug Botox ,","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"which not only comes with a laundry list of warnings","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"but has also been known to spark botulism symptoms","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"that killed several Americans .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"Scientists have approved hydroxychloroquine for 70 years ;","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"every day doctors prescribe it on- and off-label .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"If Trump and his doctor think","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"it ' s okay for him to take it ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"that ' s his business .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"Whether hydroxychloroquine will be useful in this particular fight is yet to be determined .","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"But COVID-19 aside ,","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"the drug doesn ' t \" kill people. \"","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"It saves people .","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"The fearmongering isn ' t helping anyone .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":121,"right":222,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":115,"right":120,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":115,"left":114,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":113,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":117,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":116,"right":6,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":119,"left":118,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":222,"left":139,"right":221,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":139,"left":124,"right":138,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":10,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":11,"right":122,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":138,"left":127,"right":137,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":126,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":16,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":129,"right":136,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":18,"right":128,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"elaborat